name: Personalised A3 Posters
description:
Sally Beerworth (the lady who writes all our stuff) is taking orders for one off posters.

The photos here are examples of ones she has done for people.

You can order a ONE OFF poster for any occasion: wedding, birthday, retirement, kids, new home, mother's day or just because.

HOW IT WORKS
All you need to do is place an order and  then Sally will email you asking the following questions so she can write something for you:

1   What's the occasion?

2   What do I need to know about the recipient e.g. they love wine or
     chocolate or they never cook or they are 40?

3   Anything else? e.g. they love the colour pink?

You will get a slogan to approve before we print and send.

Delivery in the UK will take 5-7 days. Or  2 weeks outside of UK to receive your poster.

The posters come in 3 different sizes and fit standard frames from the Swedish people.
